rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Liberalitas so out of way, it huge pain
to get there!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But it all worthwhile when Kurukuru
deliver letters. Kurukuru get to see
smiles like sunbeams!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So Kurukuru not mind waiting for
hours at port. Lots of free naptime
between deliveries!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0101
rows.name:
You same Rex that sending allowances
to village?

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0105
rows.name:
That's me. I'm guessing you're the
one that delivers them?

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0102
rows.name:
Not Kurukuru. Deliverer of allowances
is brilliant youngster famous among
couriers.

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0103
rows.name:
But Kurukuru delivering food of 
Correl to Avaritia!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0104
rows.name:
No direct shipping from here, though,
so it never fresh as it could be. Very
sad...

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0106
rows.name:
Considering the distances involved,
there's not much we can do.
So no point in worrying about it.
